---
import Page from "../../layouts/Page.astro";
---

<Page title="Agentic AI | Botify Life" description="Create and manage Agentic AI workflows easily with Botify Life.">
  <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto py-16 px-4">
    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-blue-700 mb-6 text-center">
      Build Agentic AI Workflows Effortlessly
    </h1>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-8 text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      Botify Life makes it easy to create, deploy, and manage Agentic AI workflows. Use our powerful MCP Server Tool to orchestrate agents, automate complex tasks, and streamline your business—all with a simple, reliable, and intuitive platform.
    </p>
    <ul class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-12">
      <li class="bg-blue-50 rounded-xl p-6 shadow flex flex-col items-center text-center">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-diagram-project text-3xl text-blue-500 mb-3"></i>
        <span class="font-semibold text-blue-700 mb-1">Easy Workflow Creation</span>
        <span class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Design and launch AI-powered workflows in minutes—no coding required.</span>
      </li>
      <li class="bg-blue-50 rounded-xl p-6 shadow flex flex-col items-center text-center">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-server text-3xl text-blue-500 mb-3"></i>
        <span class="font-semibold text-blue-700 mb-1">MCP Server Tool</span>
        <span class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Leverage the MCP Server Tool to connect, coordinate, and scale your agents seamlessly.</span>
      </li>
      <li class="bg-blue-50 rounded-xl p-6 shadow flex flex-col items-center text-center">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check text-3xl text-blue-500 mb-3"></i>
        <span class="font-semibold text-blue-700 mb-1">Simple & Reliable</span>
        <span class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Enjoy a robust, user-friendly experience with dependable results every time.</span>
      </li>
    </ul>
    <div class="text-center">
      <a href="/signup" class="inline-block px-8 py-3 rounded-xl bg-blue-600 text-white font-semibold shadow hover:bg-blue-700 transition">
        Start Creating Agentic AI Workflows
      </a>
    </div>
  </main>